relatedBlades.title: Cloudflare Zero Trust
relatedBlades.subtitle: The fastest Zero Trust application access and Internet browsing platform
relatedBlades.copy: Increase visibility, eliminate complexity, and reduce risks for remote and office users alike. Stop data loss, malware and phishing, and secure users, applications, and devices.

subMenuItems.linkText: EMA Report: Availability and Buying Options in the Emerging SASE Market
Omdia Market Radar: Zero Trust Access
Gartner® Hype Cycle™ for Network Security, 2021

features.title: Excessive trust.
features.description: The traditional tools used to connect employees to corporate apps grant excessive trust, exposing you to potential data loss.

features.title: Way too complex.
features.description: The corporate perimeter has become more difficult to control with complex, conflicting configurations across your VPNs, firewalls, proxies, and identity providers.

features.title: Blind too often.
features.description: It's never been harder to parse out logs, and make sense of how users access sensitive data.

relatedBlades.title: Zero Trust platform
relatedBlades.copy:
- One uniform and composable platform for easy setup and operations.
- Single-pass inspection for all traffic to ensure consistent, high speed protections.
- 100% uptime SLA for paid plans that only an Anycast architecture can deliver.
relatedBlades.subheadline: Verify, filter, isolate, inspect on all devices you manage, and even devices you don't.

imageAssetFile.title: Cloudflare Zero Trust marketecture graphic (lt blue bg)

relatedBlades.title: Replace or augment your VPN
relatedBlades.copy:
- Protect applications with identity, posture, and context-driven rules
- Enforce consistent default-deny, least privilege access controls across cloud, on-premise and SaaS applications
- Integrate flexibly your preferred identity and endpoint security provider
relatedBlades.subheadline: Zero Trust access for any user to any application
relatedBlades.button1Text: Learn how with our ZTNA service

relatedBlades.title: Protect users and data from Internet threats
relatedBlades.copy:
- Block phishing and malware before they strike
- Isolate browsing activity from corporate endpoints
- Start with DNS filtering to achieve quick time-to-value for remote or office users. Deliver more comprehensive security with HTTP inspection and isolation for all Internet activity.
relatedBlades.subheadline: Filter, inspect, and isolate Internet-bound traffic.
relatedBlades.button1Text: Learn how with our Secure Web Gateway

relatedBlades.title: Demo: Connect and secure any user with Cloudflare Zero Trust
relatedBlades.copy: In this nine-minute tour of Cloudflare Zero Trust, you'll see the behind-the-scenes admin setup and live end user experience for use cases like endpoint security posture enforcement, identity-based Zero Trust rules, and protection from zero-day threats.
relatedBlades.button1Text: Or take an interactive, self-guided tour

relatedBlades.quote: "Cloudflare's Zero Trust services enabled us to protect our remote-first, globally distributed workforce and critical internal applications that are not exposed to the public Internet."

quoteCarousel.quote: "At Delivery Hero, we always strive to deliver an amazing experience to our customers. Cloudflare Access helps us do the same for our internal teams: offering them a secure working environment, and removing the need for a VPN to access all of our applications across the globe."

"OneTrust relies on Cloudflare to maintain our network perimeter, so we can focus on delivering technology that helps our customers be more trusted. With Cloudflare, we can easily build context-aware Zero Trust policies for secure access to our developer tools. Employees can connect to the tools they need so simply teams don't even know Cloudflare is powering the backend. It just works."

"JetBlue Travel Products needed a way to give crew-members secure and simple access to internally-managed benefit apps. Cloudflare Zero Trust Services gave us all that and more - a much more efficient way to connect business partners and crew-members to critical internal tools."

"Cloudflare Access saved us from having to develop our own Identity and Access Management (IAM) system. We don't have to build user permission functions into the apps that Access protects. We went all in; everyone in the company has a seat."

"Zero Trust is very important, but it's also incredibly difficult to implement. The only way ezCater can succeed with this is to have the right partner. Cloudflare has given us the foundation for a successful Zero Trust implementation."

"IT is evolving by leaps and bounds, and more sophisticated, more destructive cyber threats are emerging every day. Zero Trust is the only viable security model in this environment, and Cloudflare is making it a lot easier for eTeacher Group to get there."

"Discord is where the world builds relationships. Cloudflare Zero Trust Services helps us deliver on that mission, connecting our internal engineering team to the tools they need. With Cloudflare, we can rest easy knowing every request to our critical apps is evaluated for identity and context - a true Zero Trust approach."

"POLITICO needed a way to control access to specific critical resources without the risk and overhead of connecting through a private corporate network. Cloudflare Access aligns with how and where our team works, while helping us embrace a Zero Trust security model, where every request to every app is evaluated for user identity - and no VPN is required."
quoteCarousel.quoteTitle: Senior Director, Technology Operations and Cybersecurity

features.title: 80% less time spent resolving IT tickets and security posture for employees.
91% reduction in attack surface by placing Cloudflare in front of application access and Internet browsing.
2X cost savings from reduced IT efforts.
30 minutes of setup time to unlock faster, safer Internet and application access.

relatedBlades.title: One easy-to-use platform
relatedBlades.copy:
- One dashboard unifies 7 formerly-distinct security capabilities: Secure Web Gateway, DNS Filtering, Zero Trust Network Access, VPN, Cloud Access Security Broker, Firewall as-a-service, Browser Isolation 
- Built natively from the ground up with consistent design principles: no lifting, shifting, acquisition or integration involved

relatedBlades.title: Fastest performance on largest global network
relatedBlades.copy:
- All services are <50ms from 95% of Internet users
- Routes requests faster, utilizing optimized, intelligence-driven routing
- Anycast network across %{DataCenterCount} locations with 100% SLA uptime, %{NetworkCapacity} capacity, and 1.1.1.1 — the world's fastest DNS resolver

relatedBlades.title: Simple, effective threat defense
relatedBlades.copy:
- Keeps known and unknown threats on all sites faraway from all devices
- DDoS resistant to the largest volumetric attacks
- Threat intelligence derived from %{DNSQueriesPerDay}B+ daily DNS requests and millions of Internet properties on Cloudflare's network
